y":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"法比先係role model"},{"pid":"d2cc00158098c906d05519088021a9ea0ac6e229","tid":1178912,"uid":48074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"點睇巴神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435091cf56507c4300328a6a33ff2ef5fa18f5a0","tid":1178912,"uid":204475,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:18:54.000Z","msg":"偏偏四強佢嗰下犯規係極度致命，結果自己無得打決賽。有d嘢，人算不如天算，<br />\n<br />\n同埋講生涯規劃，高拿完勝佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科隆、拜仁、祖記、多蒙特，全部都一步步去做，由中遊到國內班霸再到最top聯賽班霸，返到多蒙特養老之餘又可做埋大佬<br />\n榮譽一個比一個勁，德甲、意甲、歐協、歐聯<br />\n又保到正選又贏晒榮譽，兼且踢埋小型世界盃，歐聯歐協世界盃歐國盃全部攞過，波歷克邊有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be144fbc06f2d7461ca3ac199315cfa254a101cb","tid":1178912,"uid":27485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:23:36.000Z","msg":"依家去大會坐搵既錢<br />\n可能係中下游打幾年先有"},{"pid":"3c107150f4a88934857803c38ae12bd8aac93bdd","tid":1178912,"uid":47265,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b9d20f0e8e4efc83605d350d5c6e052dea87ec2b","tid":1178912,"uid":79562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"499640cae1c23194aa1f89930a0429bc1138a345","tid":1178912,"uid":165817,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"3dd1700307f57ce3c8dc07253f06c35144bc7ee0","tid":1178912,"uid":174530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"牙朗？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"除非你真係美斯C朗朗尼尼馬呢啲億分之一 極度天生異稟嘅天才<br />\n如果唔係 我覺得普遍正常球員17,18歲就去曼聯巴塞呢啲大球會 唔係一個十分好嘅決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"坐多過踢<br />\n大會成績行出 肯用細路博？<br />\n正選又爭唔贏 為名聲而玩壞自己前程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T18:24:22.000Z","msg":"牙朗岩岩去到曼聯果兩季都.......插花完全唔實際<br />\n